title: President Serzh Sargsyan holds reception in honor of participants of international conference convened by RA ...
text: ( Source : The President of the Republic of Armenia ) President Serzh Sargsyan held a reception today in honor of the participants of the 20th Yerevan International Conference devoted to the 20th anniversary of the Constitution of the Republic
